{Speech 1}{}{Pre-dialog setup}
{Speech 2}{}{Hi@@How's it going?@@Everything alright?@@What do you want?@@Arroyo's a cool town@@The evil writers haven't written me a dialog yet@@Sorry, I've got nothing to say to you@@Boo!@@Bah!@@One, one.@@One, two, three.@@Hello, Wasteland! This is President John Henry Eden speaking. Wait, I'm blowing my cover.@@She sells seashells by the seashore.@@The Chosen crossed the river, dipped his hand in the river...@@I don't have a dialog yet@@Go away, we've got nothing to talk about@@Get lost@@Begone@@Tata!@@How're things?@@Don't make trouble here@@Arroyo's a peaceful village@@Peace!@@Make yourself at home@@Jabaduba!}
